{
	"_readme": "V20 function-preserving capacity branch from the shared wide256 reach-30-critic warm-up. Net2Wider expands trunk 256x256 to 512x512 and value/aux heads 128 to 256 without changing initial outputs. Pair against fair-v19-solo-cont-control through generation 5: seeds, source games, fixed 120000-row PPO budget, optimizer steps, rewards, and decoding are identical. This is a development experiment only; no solo checkpoint is promotion-eligible without multiplayer, held-out, and human gates.",
